sentences: Thomas Bredahl (born 2 November 1980) is a Danish music manager, former guitarist and singer.
Bredahl joined Volbeat in 2006, and the band announced his departure on November 28, 2011.

He was lead guitarist of Volbeat and is now the guitarist of Gob Squad.
